description:
RealSimpleEDU.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for "Organic Chemistry"

App is continuously updated based on your feedback.

App offers 22 interactive tutorials with search feature.


Includes following Tutorials:

Wonders of Organic World,
Hydrocarbons,
Classification,
Reaction Mechanisms,
Functional Groups,
The Periodic Table,
Organic Acids and Bases,
Chemical Bonding I,
Chemical Bonding II,
Organic Structures,
Drawing Resonance Structures,
Isomerism and Types,
Alkanes and Nomenclature,
Alkenes and Nomenclature,
Alkynes and Nomenclature,
Alcohols and Nomenclature,
Aldehydes,
Ketones,
Methods of Purification,
Chromatography and Types,
Organometallic Chemistry,
Important Concepts.



Includes following Quizzes:

Quiz on Hydrocarbons and Classification,
Quiz on Reaction Mechanisms, Functional Groups and Periodic Table,
Quiz on Organic Acids, Bases and Chemical Bonding,
Quiz on Organic and Resonance Structures,
Quiz on Isomerism, Alkanes and Alkenes,
Quiz on Alkynes, Alcohols, Aldehydes and Ketones.



Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.

Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.

Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
